body:
The following syntax demonstrates how to run a query against a field
indexed for Automated Embedding:

```json
{
  "$vectorSearch": {
    "index": "<index-name>",
    "limit": <number-of-results>,
    "numCandidates": <number-of-candidates>,
    "path": "<field-to-search>",
    "query": "<query-string>"
  }
}
```
